biotools.summary: TripletGO is an algorithm for predicting Gene Ontology (GO) of genes. It consists of four pipelines to detect GO terms through (1) expression profile similarity based on triplet network, (2) genetic sequence alignment, (3) protein sequence alignment, and (4) naïve probability. The final function insights are a combination of the four pipelines through neural network
